data.description: Ask seller about a 2-1 buy down credit. This charming single-family home is sure to be the perfect fit for you. Its natural color palette and fresh interior paint create a warm and inviting atmosphere. The main living space features a cozy fireplace and is perfect for entertaining. The flexible living space includes other rooms for a variety of uses. The primary bathroom features a separate tub and shower, double sinks, and good under sink storage. The backyard has a sitting area for enjoying the outdoors. This property has all the features youare looking for and more. Donat miss out on this amazing opportunity.
